                text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/emma/level1/emmaFrontMorning-10.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Emma stares out the window at the street, coffee cup in hand, not really seeing anything.<</narrative>>

