<<dialog "dinerWaitress1">>This machine's been dying for a month.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Sounds like it's on its last legs.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress1">>Just like me. We're bonding.<</dialog>>
